metadata.name: Broken Face Digital Melt
metadata.description:
@46thexposure presents Broken Face #2 From #46 Unique Pieces of Digital Art!

Broken Face Digital Melt features a unique 9534 x 7627 px Melted Glasses and Neon Signs.

We are @46thexposure!
Our Mission is to create The First Metaverse Virtual Exhibition!

The first Broken Face NFT Collection will have 46 Unique NFT pieces and they will serve as Passes for Future Events and Exhibitions!
